  "description": "This individual is a middle-aged human of solid, service-hardened build, marked by taupe skin and brown eyes set beneath heavy lids shaped by long hours of close work. Brown hair is kept in a plain, practical cut that emphasizes a broad brow and a square jaw. Fine lines gather at the mouth and eyes in the durable pattern of habitual conversation and measured attention. The hands are thick-fingered and callused, consistent with a profession defined by constant handling of glass, cask, and coin.",
